<i>adverb</i>: 한갓되이 [한갇뙤이/한갇뛔이] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>한갓되이 [한갇뙤이/한갇뛔이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. triflingly; insignificantly</dd><br>
<dd>중요하거나 특별할 것이 없어 겨우 하찮은 것밖에 안 되게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of considering something merely trivial without anything important or special.</dd><br>
<dd>2. vainly; fruitlessly</dd><br>
<dd>아무런 보람이나 실속이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of bearing no fruit or having no substance.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>